LeetCode Problem 1068 – Product Sales Analysis I
 Day 25 / 30 Days Challenge 🚀
Problem Summary
You are given two tables:
Sales
 | sale_id | product_id | year | quantity | price |
Product
 | product_id | product_name |
You need to report:
product_name
year
price
by joining the Sales and Product tables.

SQL Solution

SELECT 
 p.product_name,
 s.year,
 s.price
FROM Sales s
JOIN Product p
ON s.product_id = p.product_id;

Explanation
Sales s → contains product_id, year, and price.
Product p → contains product_id and product_name.
JOIN both tables using product_id.
Select:
product_name from Product
year and price from Sales
